                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9764" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2448</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">572 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">穿越周期，基业长青：中通快递数字物流开启“加速度”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Navigating Cycles and Achieving Long-Term Success: ZTO Express&#39; Digital Logistics Accelerates</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蒲丹琳，李昕冉，姜琳</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中通快递股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化转型；智慧物流；价值创造</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digital transformation; Smart logistics; Value creation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在数字化浪潮席卷各行各业的背景下，物流行业正迎来转型升级的新机遇。政府政策的支持加速了数字经济与实体经济的深度融合，推动物流行业向智能化、柔性化方向发展。然而，我国物流行业仍面临“大而不强”的挑战，如何借助数字化手段实现降本增效、提升企业竞争力，成为行业亟待解决的问题。作为行业龙头，中通快递率先布局数字化转型，通过智慧物流体系的构建，不断优化资源配置、提升运营效率，并推动创新发展。本案例聚焦中通快递的数字化转型实践，探索其在数据驱动、管理优化、业务模式创新等方面的举措，引导学员思考数字化如何成为企业价值创造的重要引擎并借鉴中通快递的实践经验，加深对数字化转型战略与实施路径的认知，得出相应启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Amid the sweeping digital wave across various industries, the logistics sector is embracing new opportunities for transformation and upgrading. Government policies have accelerated the deep integration of the digital economy with the real economy, driving the logistics industry toward greater intelligence and flexibility. However, China’s logistics sector still faces the challenge of being “large but not strong.” How to leverage digital tools to reduce costs, enhance efficiency, and improve corporate competitiveness has become a pressing issue for the industry. As a leading company in the sector, ZTO Express has taken the lead in digital transformation, continuously optimizing resource allocation, improving operational efficiency, and driving innovation through the development of an intelligent logistics system.  
This case study focuses on ZTO Express’s digital transformation practices, analyzing its exploration in data-driven decision-making, management optimization, and business model innovation. It aims to guide learners in understanding how digitalization serves as a key driver of value creation and to draw insights from ZTO Express’s experience, deepening their understanding of digital transformation strategies and implementation pathways.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司战略》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化转型；资源基础理论（Resource-Based View, RBV）;波特价值链分析理论（Porter’s Value Chain Analysis）;价值创造理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
